cebook.com/9holiday/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F9holiday%2F&d=5kcKS88VDqQHtVy1SgIa4Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c9d24d18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/9holiday/</a><br />\n<br />\n或者係facebook直接search 鳩假期<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 鳩假期打手，大家快啲like"},{"pid":"23ccb0b3657c9ff49b69c4ccdb1d8f0553d142cb","tid":262793,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>記者點評：家的味道<br />\n<br />\n這裏的粽子吃起來並沒有驚為天人的獨特味道，反而像小時候媽媽包粽的味道，是小店、是家的味道。有時候不需要太過花巧的配料，簡單的鹹蛋黃、肥豬肉、綠豆，便已經足夠。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/-2017-05-16-4.52.53_279122119591aca6de1251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F-2017-05-16-4.52.53_279122119591aca6de1251&d=5kcKS88VDqQHtVy1SgIa4Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a9c4ed0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/-2017-05-16-4.52.53_279122119591aca6de1251</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.weekendhk.com/-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8F%B0%E8%8C%B6-%E6%B0%B4%E6%9E%9C%E8%8C%B6-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%8E%83%E8%A1%97/5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%258C%25B6-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%259E%259C%25E8%258C%25B6-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%258E%2583%25E8%25A1%2597%2F5%2F&d=5kcKS88VDqQHtVy1SgIa4Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=de0fad7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.weekendhk.com/-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8F%B0%E8%8C%B6-%E6%B0%B4%E6%9E%9C%E8%8C%B6-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%8E%83%E8%A1%97/5/</a></blockquote><br />\n點解用筷子用到咁樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒撚左條女佢喇筷子都唔識揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢fb 篇屌讀者文先過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同求<br />\n啲內容文筆垃圾到閪咁仲好意思屌番啲讀者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLiuchingman Mandy<br />\n兩年了。<br />\n<br />\n由最初的nobody，每條feed只得十幾like，到現在百多萬fan base，每一個字都有海量haters在虎視眈眈，才兩年，就有這麼大轉變，是兩年前的我絕對想像不了的。<br />\n<br />\n還記得第一日入職，回家就已經跟家人說我想辭職，結果一做就做到現在，還把大學同學、小學同學都帶到這間公司，進入了無限OT的輪迴。<br />\n<br />\n過去兩年，幾乎可以接觸的題材都接觸過，飲飲食食、上天下海、美勞手作、郊遊玩樂都做勻，以一間大公司來說，算有很高自由度，只要落多點嘴頭，編輯便會放手讓我去做想做的題材。打呢份工，的確試了很多新奇又有趣的玩意。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，芝士紫薯抹茶完全不是我的菜，既然無法控制大眾的喜好，只能告訴自己在做稿的時候不要迷失自己，追數的同時亦要追質素，問心無愧就好。<br />\n<br />\n#多謝新假期 #報邊死邊 #所有小店都會執笠 #全香港都會淪陷 #鍵盤戰士出名會養起晒所有小店 #全港啲路都寫咗你名 #你去就得人哋去就唔得 #幼稚園都識不要亂拋垃圾但你唔識 #殺人放火都係我哋教 #我明㗎我真係明 #特別係當你同公司靠你賺錢養佢嘅嗰班人都不斷出片抽你水 #你就知道千錯萬錯都係我錯<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：新假期 #sor無授權係偷相"},{"pid":"99fefae64244171464f60b8569c78d3d5360b9c5","tid":262793,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:24:13.000Z","msg":"霉體新假期妓者不意外"}]}